description: You will find that it's getting harder and harder to find a mini-USB cables these days, However some devices still need the Mini-B input, and sometimes you want to reach things that are far away while still being plugged in, AllEasy will continue to offer this Mini USB power cord for people who still want to connect your 5 pin Mini-B cable to your digital camera or PS3 handler and more devices with the USB Mini-B port. 1. 15 feet cable( LONGER than most other brand cable): Allows you reach things that are far away while still being plugged in 2. Constructed with corrosion-resistant, gold-plated and well protected connectors for optimal signal clarity and shielding to minimize interference 3. Connect peripherals that require a Mini-B connection to your computer -Astro A40/50 -Nikon DSLR -SanDisk Sansa MP3 player -GoPro HERO4/HERO3/HD HERO2/HD HERO -Canon PowerShot A310/A400/A460/A470/A560/A570 IS/A580/A590 IS/A650 IS/A75/A85/A95/S50/S60/S70/S80/S100/S110/S410/S500/S2 IS/S3 IS and so on -Lenght:15 Feet -Connector A:USB2.0 A Male -Connector B:USB2.0 Mini B (5-pin) Male -USB 1.0 compliant -Data transfor rate up to 480Mbps -Gold plated connectors 1. This is a Mini-B USB Cable, not a Micro Cable, please note that there are many types of USB connectors, make sure that you fully understand what kinds of cable you need, this cable do ONLY work on devices with USB Mini-B port 2. The difference between Mini-B and Micro-B is that the Micro-B is half as thick while the width is the same----Mini-B is 3x7mm / Micro-B is 1.5x7mm 3.The maximum length for a single USB cable is 15ft. To get more than 15 ft. you will need to boost the signal with a repeater Cable
